data.description:
Gorgeous brand new & move-in ready Perry Homes 3 bed, 2 bath home for rent. Never lived in, be the first to enjoy this beautiful new home! Flowing floor plan with sweeping views from the front door all the way through to the back patio. Open living, dining and kitchen with lots of natural light, perfect for families and entertaining. Neutral warm grey color palette throughout waiting for a personalized touch. Spacious kitchen with white shaker cabinets, large grey accent color island, popular subway tile backsplash, pantry and new appliances. Huge master retreat with spacious en suite bath featuring dual vanities, standing shower, garden tub and walk-in closet. Secluded secondary bedrooms with private bath. Convenient mud room entry from garage with separate utility with room for fridge.
Public Driving Directions:	I-30 East, exit East US HWY 80, continue for approximately 13 miles and take exit for FM 548. Turn left at FM 548 and continue for approximately 2.5 miles.

New home 2022 never lived in 

Need immediate occupancy
